data: First day of school for Grade nines only! Grade nines will get to meet their teachers, explore the school, and check out the many clubs of RHHS!
Mandatory information session regarding StuCo grade representative and mascot elections.
Candidates for the grade representative and mascot positions will campaign for the election at the end of the week.
Vote for your StuCo grade representatives and mascots for the 2024-2025 school year!

Bring your blankets and your friends and snuggle in for an exciting nighttime viewing of Inside Out 2. Snacks and drinks will be available for purchase and activities will be run before 7PM. There will also be a club fair from 3:30 to 5:00.
